Step1:Divide Step2:Conquer 
(Old videos) March 2020(first week of the virus): I walked in a whole foods yesterday everyone in there was wearing a mask except a few workers and me, the song stand by me was playing. I wanted to cry. Fuck this “virus” people were already scared of each other before now it’s gotten too extreme, and this is just the beginning. May Yah have mercy on our sins, ignorance, and stupidity.

-Second video: listen closely to the lyrics, this song is completely based on the Bible.
